title: The Belle Delphine Mystery & Our New Studio - H3 Podcast # 246
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast OFF THE RAILS Ethan & the boys are back IN STUDIO for the first time since a global pandemic sent us into exile. We talk Faze Blanks having hot dogs for brains, Chrissy Teigen being awful, UFO's being "real" according to Big Ed's cousin, Bryce Hall vs Austin "STOP" McBroom, and a whole lot more!
